or the universe.</p><h2 class="mume-header" id="quick-start">Quick Start</h2><h3 class="mume-header" id="create-a-new-post">Create a new post</h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="bash" class="language-bash">$ hexo new <span class="token string">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></pre><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html">Writing</a></p><h3 class="mume-header" id="run-server">Run server</h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="bash" class="language-bash">$ hexo server</pre><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/server.html">Server</a></p><h3 class="mume-header" id="generate-static-files">Generate static files</h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="bash" class="language-bash">$ hexo generate</pre><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html">Generating</a></p><h3 class="mume-header" id="deploy-to-remote-sites">Deploy to remote sites</h3><pre data-role="codeBlock" data-info="bash" class="language-bash">$ hexo deploy</pre><p>More info: <a href="https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html">Deployment</a></p>      </div>                                                  </body></html>]]></content>
    
    
    
